{"tid":1477183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【文革之罪恶－－反革命听见罪】","createTime":"2019-08-16T04:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T05:15:17.000Z","uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1abf84734837d25b9440e92c0e7039241c937844","tid":1477183,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUBXHT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUBXHT.png&h=318d3302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海某歌舞团舞蹈演员姚元清与同事等五人聊天，一位同事对她说：&ldquo;刘少奇是好人，他是被冤枉的。&rdquo;<br />\n姚元清当时保持了沉默，没有表达意见。她的同事后来被以现行反革命罪处死，她因为在现场听见言论没有举报而被判处有期徒刑十年，罪名是&ldquo;反革命听见犯&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"26f9bd0a04f14d623d350ab7e061e21c0b935c74","tid":1477183,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:02:43.000Z","msg":"盲嘅都俾人話偷睇國家機密<br />\n何況你係隔離聽到人講"},{"pid":"9bd9c94f18edb05120b3d355678adef371997872","tid":1477183,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"。"}]}